location.Description: Location of the PowerBI Dedicated resource.

tags.Description: Key-value pairs of additional resource provisioning properties.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

sku.Description: Represents the SKU name and Azure pricing tier for PowerBI Dedicated capacity resource.

createdBy.Description: An identifier for the identity that created the resource

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource. Possible values include: 'User', 'Application', 'ManagedIdentity', 'Key'

lastModifiedBy.Description: An identifier for the identity that last modified the resource

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that last modified the resource. Possible values include: 'User', 'Application', 'ManagedIdentity', 'Key'

lastModifiedAt.Description: The timestamp of resource last modification (UTC)

tier.Description: The name of the Azure pricing tier to which the SKU applies. Possible values include: 'PBIE_Azure', 'Premium', 'AutoPremiumHost'

administration.Description: An array of administrator user identities

mode.Description: The capacity mode. Possible values include: 'Gen1', 'Gen2'

state.Description: The current state of PowerBI Dedicated resource. The state is to indicate more states outside of resource provisioning. Possible values include: 'Deleting', 'Succeeded', 'Failed', 'Paused', 'Suspended', 'Provisioning', 'Updating', 'Suspending', 'Pausing', 'Resuming', 'Preparing', 'Scaling'

provisioningState.Description: The current deployment state of PowerBI Dedicated resource. The provisioningState is to indicate states for resource provisioning. Possible values include: 'Deleting', 'Succeeded', 'Failed', 'Paused', 'Suspended', 'Provisioning', 'Updating', 'Suspending', 'Pausing', 'Resuming', 'Preparing', 'Scaling'

members.Description: An array of administrator user identities.

location.Description: Location of the PowerBI Dedicated resource.

tags.Description: Key-value pairs of additional resource provisioning properties.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

sku.Description: Represents the SKU name and Azure pricing tier for auto scale v-core resource.

properties.Description: Properties of an auto scale v-core resource.

tier.Description: The name of the Azure pricing tier to which the SKU applies. Possible values include: 'AutoScale'

capacity.Description: The capacity of an auto scale v-core resource.

capacityLimit.Description: The maximum capacity of an auto scale v-core resource.

capacityObjectId.Description: The object ID of the capacity resource associated with the auto scale v-core resource.

provisioningState.Description: The current deployment state of an auto scale v-core resource. The provisioningState is to indicate states for resource provisioning. Possible values include: 'Succeeded'
